.SYNOPSIS
    This PowerShell script ensures that DoD Root CA certificates are installed in the Windows Trusted Root Certification Authorities store. 
    This allows Windows to:
   🔹 Trust DoD-issued certificates
   🔹 Validate secure TLS connections to DoD systems
   🔹 Authenticate secure services (web portals, email, VPN, etc.)

